  "title": "F&B Service Crew Islandwide | Up to $4,800 | Training Provided",
  "description": "<h2><strong>🐟 Join Tai Er – Home of Famous Fish Sauerkraut!</strong></h2><p>Looking for a fun F&B job with <strong>good pay, full meals, and real career growth</strong>?<br /><strong>Tai Er (MNC F&B)</strong> is hiring <strong>islandwide</strong> — no experience needed, we’ll train you!</p><p>📍 Islandwide, Singapore<br />🍽 Non-Halal | Chinese Cuisine<br />🎓 Training Provided</p><h2><strong>💼 Open Positions</strong></h2><p>🔹 <strong>Service</strong> <strong>Crew</strong></p><ul><li>Full-Time (6 days): <strong>$3,250 – $3,500</strong></li><li>Part-Time (3 days / Half-day): <strong>$1,750 – $1,900</strong></li></ul><p>🔹 <strong>Management Trainee</strong></p><ul><li><strong>$3,200 – $3,500</strong></li></ul><p>🔹 <strong>Outlet Manager </strong></p><ul><li><strong>Up to $4,800</strong></li></ul><h2><strong>🎁 Why You’ll Love It</strong></h2><p>✔️ <strong>3 Family Meals Daily</strong> 🥢<br />✔️ Attendance Allowance<br />✔️ Medical Claims<br />✔️ Referral Rewards<br />✔️ Career Progression 🚀<br />✔️ Fun & Friendly Colleagues</p><h2><strong>✅ What you'll be doing</strong></h2><p>✨Provides excellent customer service to all guests<br />✨Set up restaurant according to SOPs<br />✨Serving food and beverages<br />✨Clear and sanitise tables<br />✨Maintaining counters clean and tidy</p><h2><strong>✅ We’re Looking For</strong></h2><p>✔️ Friendly & customer-focused<br />✔️ Positive attitude, team player<br />✔️ Can work shifts, weekends & PH<br />✔️ Ability to read and converse in Mandarin is an advantage (to understand Mandarin order chits and communicate with kitchen staff and customers)<br />✔️ F&B experience = bonus (not required!)</p><p>✨ Come work, eat well, and grow with Tai Er.<br /><strong>Apply now</strong> — your next F&B adventure starts here! 😄🐟</p>",
